{"tid":531900,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃之鋒黃浩銘申請暫緩執行刑期被拒即時還押","createTime":"2018-01-17T09:34:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-17T11:09:54.000Z","uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6445dfaab30af076fa8f6e3b95b36d2e03055ed4","tid":531900,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T09:34:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1375702_1_20180117172212.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1375702_1_20180117172212.jpg&h=9ec7db4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2014年佔領行動期間，16人刑事藐視法庭罪成，其中兩名被告黃浩銘和黃之鋒，分別被判入獄4個月15日及3個月。兩人申請暫緩執行刑期，被高等法院拒絕，需要還押。<br />\n<br />\n法官陳慶偉在庭上，詢問控辯雙方，法庭是否有權處理暫緩刑期申請，又說如果兩人希望申請保釋，可向上訴庭申請。<br />\n<br />\n陳慶偉說，兩人的申請，原意與申請保釋無分別，而根據有關法例，有關刑事藐視法庭的罪行，申請保釋需要由上訴庭處理，因此拒絕兩人的申請。<br />\n<br />\n同案的岑敖暉被判入獄1個月、緩刑12個月及罰款1萬元；其餘13名被告，分別被判緩刑及罰款。"},{"pid":"ca5f8811b4c8d687c4f501e086bb50341eed55df","tid":531900,"uid":132038,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T10:56:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c7c27ccbc5622f2351df8da2b501249129f15145","tid":531900,"uid":44358,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"ca5f8811b4c8d687c4f501e086bb50341eed55df","tid":531900,"uid":132038,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T10:56:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T11:01:45.000Z","msg":"你老母今晚做雞接客，冇時間睇住你做功課<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33adb427ec9f4a9ff67fb48cbbe707306631230f","tid":531900,"uid":132038,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T11:07:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a95724dad1d372559b0c27604e09c4d7e47cd0e8","tid":531900,"uid":55488,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T11:09:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3d6f2525921349cf77dfd7f2778ca1fe896e522c","tid":531900,"uid":23160,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T11:09:54.000Z","msg":"黃浩銘恨到啦<br />\n下次就可以講坐左幾耐"}]}